PARIS, Jan. 13. -- Prince Philippe Marie Alphonse de Bourbon of the two Sicilies, son of Count de Caserta, married today Princess Marie Louis d'Orleans, daughter of the Duke de Vendome, at the home of the latter in Neuilly. The ceremony was strictly private. View Full Article in Timesmachine Â»
